        <Parent_String>embroidering [300053653], needleworking (process) [300053652], needleworking and needleworking techniques [300239671], textile working processes and techniques [300239670], textile processes and techniques [300239669], processes and techniques by material [300053900], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
